# Puddles design implementation

When implementing from Figma for this repo:

- **Fonts:** Nunito Sans for UI; header wordmark uses Quicksand + Comfortaa only in `BrandLockup`.
- **Tokens:** Prefer variables in `src/index.css` (`--color-brand`, `--gradient-chrome`, `--shadow-elevation-light-3`, `--radius-card`, etc.) over hardcoded values.
- **Components:** Reuse `AppHeader`, `Footer`, `CommunityCtaCard`, `PageContainer`, `VisualPlaceholders`, and existing button classes (`btn-primary`, `btn-utility`).
- **Cards:** Use `.elevation-light-3` for Airbnb-style elevation; avoid pastel card backgrounds.
- **Layout:** Match page top offset with `pt-6 md:pt-10` on Discovery and About unless Figma specifies otherwise.
- **Scope:** Implement only the requested page/section; do not refactor unrelated pages.
